about.summary: A suite of convenience functions for exploring water data in a Jupyter Notebook

name: hydrofunctions
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.1.7" %}

package:
  name: hydrofunctions
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/h/hydrofunctions/hydrofunctions-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6d7c9eff8ee0ff4a365126649236fe5b4285a12eaff1584bd50020a7a8b4471d

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - ipython
    - matplotlib
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - requests

test:
  imports:
    - hydrofunctions
  requires:
    - coverage

about:
  home: https://github.com/mroberge/hydrofunctions
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "A suite of convenience functions for exploring water data in a Jupyter Notebook"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
